Concepts you should try to master:
    If you use FXML, some MVC-type idea.
    Database CRUD.
    Reading and writing files. Txt, CVS, TSV, Excel, JSON, and XML.
    Task and Service
    Animation API. AnimationTimer, Timeline, and the Transitions.


