Design:

3 types of notes:
Main notes
Trash notes - removed after 7 days in trash
Locked notes

Notes can be just text & images or lists.

Reorder notes by click and drag.
Reorder items by clicking on dots and dragging

Add list on enter - text must not be empty
list options: delete, make copy, add tag, convert to list/note
